            <div type="a">
                <column>2</column>
                <head>More about High Prices</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>SS pleased to see consumers complaining about high prices for staples.
                    Consumers should just refuse to pay, and the prices will drop to a more
                    reasonable level.</summary>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
                <column>2</column>
                <head>S. M. Pettingill &amp; Co.</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>SS is praising its New York agents. Shows the contacts that Staunton had
                    with New York &amp; Philadelphia.</summary>
            </div>
